| Command | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `hexdump -C` | Display file as **hexadecimal + ASCII** |
| `head -n 10` | Show first 10 lines (text only) |
| `strings` | Extract printable strings from binary |
| `file` | Guess file type based on content |

